---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<section>
   
    <article>
      <h1>Si <span>Polimericos Dial </span>tuviera un sinonimo, sería <span>¡CALIDAD!.</span></h1>
      <p>
       <span>#1 de Colombia</span><br>
       ¿Qué esperas para contactarnos?
      </p>
      <div class="botones-art">
        <button class="cssbuttons-io">
          <span><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512"><!--!Font Awesome Free 6.5.1 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free Copyright 2024 Fonticons, Inc.--><path fill="#fff" d="M164.9 24.6c-7.7-18.6-28-28.5-47.4-23.2l-88 24C12.1 30.2 0 46 0 64C0 311.4 200.6 512 448 512c18 0 33.8-12.1 38.6-29.5l24-88c5.3-19.4-4.6-39.7-23.2-47.4l-96-40c-16.3-6.8-35.2-2.1-46.3 11.6L304.7 368C234.3 334.7 177.3 277.7 144 207.3L193.3 167c13.7-11.2 18.4-30 11.6-46.3l-40-96z"/></svg> Contactar</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </article>
    <aside>
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3977.025519565371!2d-74.10139192502142!3d4.589443195385185!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x8e3f991f50dedd15%3A0xeae481775d0f3e59!2sPOLIMERICOS%20DIAL%20DE%20COLOMBIA!5e0!3m2!1ses-419!2sco!4v1711125386418!5m2!1ses-419!2sco" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
      </aside>
  </section>
<style>
    section {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: relative;
    padding:60px 30px;
    min-height: 100vh;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: var(--white);
  }
  article {
    position: relative;
    width: 50%;
    padding: 0px 20px 20px 40px;
  }
  article h1 {
    color: var(--caoba);
    font-size: 48px;
  }
  article span {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: 900;
  }
  article p {
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    font-size: 25px;
    color: var(--caoba)
  }
  .cssbuttons-io {
    position: relative;
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    border-radius: 0.8em;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to right,
      var(--gold),
      rgba(255, 217, 0, 0.644)
    );
    color: ghostwhite;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cssbuttons-io svg {
    width: 1.2em;
    height: 1.2em;
    margin-right: 0.5em;
  }

  .cssbuttons-io span {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
    transition: color 0.4s;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 0.8em 1.2em 0.8em 1.05em;
  }

  .cssbuttons-io::before,
  .cssbuttons-io::after {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .cssbuttons-io::before {
    content: "";
    background: var(--caoba);
    width: 120%;
    left: -10%;
    transform: skew(30deg);
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.3, 1, 0.8, 1);
  }

  .cssbuttons-io:hover::before {
    transform: translate3d(100%, 0, 0);
  }

  .cssbuttons-io:active {
    transform: scale(0.95);
  }

  aside {
    width: 50%;
    padding: 20px 0;
    
    position: relative;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  aside iframe{
    border-radius: 2    0px;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }

  .icono-right{
    border: 10px solid var(--caoba);
    position: absolute;
    background-color: var(--gold);
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 100px;
    width: 100px;
    display: grid;
    place-content: center;
    border-radius: 0 35px 0 0;
    transition: .5s;
  }
  .icono-right ion-icon{
    color: white;
    font-size: 60px;
  }
  aside:hover .icono-right{
    color: white;
    background-color: var(--caoba);
    scale: 1.2;
  }

  /* Estilos para dispositivos móviles */
@media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
  section {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 50px 15px 0;
  }
  
  article {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    padding: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  aside{
    width: 100%;
    height: 360px;
    padding: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }
  
  article h1{
    font-size: 30px;
  }
  article p{
    font-size: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .cssbuttons-io {
    font-size: 14px;
  }
 
  aside {
    width: 100%;
  }
  iframe{
    border-radius: 10px;
  }
}
</style>